					<description><![CDATA[<p><img width="2560" height="1706" src="https://firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/kevin-butz-xap6BlTK2YE-unsplash-scaled.jpg" class="attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/kevin-butz-xap6BlTK2YE-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;ssl=1 2560w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/kevin-butz-xap6BlTK2YE-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=768%2C512&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/kevin-butz-xap6BlTK2YE-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=1536%2C1023&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/kevin-butz-xap6BlTK2YE-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=2048%2C1364&amp;ssl=1 2048w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/kevin-butz-xap6BlTK2YE-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=219%2C146&amp;ssl=1 219w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/kevin-butz-xap6BlTK2YE-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=2440&amp;ssl=1 2440w" sizes="(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px" /></p>
<p>火報記者 洪瑜蓉 / 綜合報導 你們有看過這麼愛耍無賴的狗狗嗎？美國一名飼主近日分享自家柴犬拒絕回家的有趣一幕 &#8230;</p>
<p>這篇文章 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw/2025/07/12/%e5%b0%b1%e6%98%af%e4%b8%8d%e6%83%b3%e5%9b%9e%e5%ae%b6%ef%bc%9f%e8%b6%85%e8%90%8c%e6%9f%b4%e7%8a%ac%e6%95%a3%e6%ad%a5%e5%88%b0%e4%b8%80%e5%8d%8a%e7%9b%b4%e6%8e%a5%e8%a3%9d%e6%ad%bb%e8%ae%93%e4%b8%bb/">就是不想回家？超萌柴犬散步到一半直接裝死讓主人超無奈 </a> 最早出現於 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw">火報</a>。</p>
]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img width="2560" height="1706" src="https://firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/kevin-butz-xap6BlTK2YE-unsplash-scaled.jpg" class="attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/kevin-butz-xap6BlTK2YE-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;ssl=1 2560w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/kevin-butz-xap6BlTK2YE-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=768%2C512&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/kevin-butz-xap6BlTK2YE-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=1536%2C1023&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/kevin-butz-xap6BlTK2YE-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=2048%2C1364&amp;ssl=1 2048w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/kevin-butz-xap6BlTK2YE-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=219%2C146&amp;ssl=1 219w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/kevin-butz-xap6BlTK2YE-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=2440&amp;ssl=1 2440w" sizes="(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px" /></p>
<p>火報記者 洪瑜蓉 / 綜合報導</p>



<p>你們有看過這麼愛耍無賴的狗狗嗎？美國一名飼主近日分享自家柴犬拒絕回家的有趣一幕，引發社群網友熱議，飼主表示愛犬不僅性格固執，還經常選擇用一種出其不意的方式來逃避回家的命運，讓他感到超無奈。&nbsp;</p>



<p>該名飼主表示，自家養的柴犬從小性格古靈精怪，不僅活力旺盛還喜歡到處搞怪，每當他帶著愛犬出門散步完後，狗狗總是能使用各種千奇百怪的招式，來表達自己還不想回家的意願，任憑主人怎麼勸和哄都沒用。&nbsp;</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img decoding="async" width="1220" height="813" src="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/jaycee-xie-aH9Uskj8XTU-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=1220%2C813&#038;ssl=1" alt="" class="wp-image-225593" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/jaycee-xie-aH9Uskj8XTU-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;ssl=1 2560w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/jaycee-xie-aH9Uskj8XTU-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=768%2C512&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/jaycee-xie-aH9Uskj8XTU-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=1536%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/jaycee-xie-aH9Uskj8XTU-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=2048%2C1365&amp;ssl=1 2048w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/jaycee-xie-aH9Uskj8XTU-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=219%2C146&amp;ssl=1 219w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/jaycee-xie-aH9Uskj8XTU-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=2440&amp;ssl=1 2440w" sizes="(max-width: 1220px) 100vw, 1220px" data-recalc-dims="1" /><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">這隻調皮的小柴犬，每次在散步完後的回家路上，總會使出各種千奇百怪的招式<br>(示意圖/Unsplash)</figcaption></figure>



<p>這天這隻調皮的小柴犬又上演著相同戲碼，牠在回家的路上突然一屁股坐在草地邊上，扭頭凝視著遠方，仿佛這麼做就好像能逃避自己回家的命運，畫面相當搞笑又令人無可奈何。&nbsp;</p>



<p>然而就當主人靠近試圖哄牠回家時，柴犬竟突然一個箭步衝向路邊的枯葉堆，緊接著直接鑽了進去，將自己完全藏在樹葉裡，絲毫不顧主人在旁邊焦急呼喚，自顧自地躲在裡面放鬆。&nbsp;</p>



<p>這隻超萌小柴犬的搞怪行為曝光後引起許多網友共鳴，不少人紛紛留言表示「跟我家的狗好像」、「柴犬不意外」、「可能再泡樹葉溫泉」、「到底多不想回家」、「好有個性和生活」。&nbsp;</p>
<p>這篇文章 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw/2025/07/12/%e5%b0%b1%e6%98%af%e4%b8%8d%e6%83%b3%e5%9b%9e%e5%ae%b6%ef%bc%9f%e8%b6%85%e8%90%8c%e6%9f%b4%e7%8a%ac%e6%95%a3%e6%ad%a5%e5%88%b0%e4%b8%80%e5%8d%8a%e7%9b%b4%e6%8e%a5%e8%a3%9d%e6%ad%bb%e8%ae%93%e4%b8%bb/">就是不想回家？超萌柴犬散步到一半直接裝死讓主人超無奈 </a> 最早出現於 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw">火報</a>。</p>
]]></content:encoded>
					
		
		
